{
  "text": "Sensory analysis. Average scores of sensory characteristics were evaluated using RSM method. The results of the analysis are shown in Table 4 . The optimal burger formulation was selected, which contained 63% of surimi and 37% of minced chicken meat. Also, based on average scores of sensory evaluation, a concentration of 500 mg/L for each EO was selected as optimal ( [CITATION_1] .",
